## Business Task

Danny opened a small Japanese restaurant in early 2021 selling his three favourite foods — sushi, curry, and ramen. He wants to understand his customers better: how often they visit, how much they spend, and which items they love the most. This information will help him decide whether to expand the loyalty program and improve the overall customer experience.

